==External links== * [http://www.intel.com/content/www/us/en/processors/architectures-software-developer-manuals.html Intel 64 and IA-32 Architectures Software Developer's Manuals] * [http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/system/platform/64bit/MCAsupport.mspx Microsoft's article on Itanium's MCA] * [http://www.mcelog.org/ Linux x86 daemon for processing of machine checks]
