'''People Pattern''' is a [[digital marketing]] company based in Austin, Texas.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.siliconhillsnews.com/2015/03/09/people-pattern-digs-marketing-data-out-of-social-media/ |title=People Pattern Digs Marketing Data Out of Social Media |publisher=Silicon Hills |date= 2015-03-09|accessdate=2015-03-09 | first=Tim | last=Green}}</ref> The company's text analytics software applications extract facts, relationships and [[sentiment analysis|sentiment]] from [[unstructured data]], which comprise approximately 85% of the information companies store electronically.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.forbes.com/2007/04/04/teradata-solution-software-biz-logistics-cx_rm_0405data.html |title=Structuring Unstructured Data |publisher=Forbes.com |date= 2007-04-05|accessdate=2010-02-24}}</ref>
Corporations that use or have used People Pattern software include [[McDonald's]], [[Charles Schwab Corporation|Charles Schwab]], [[Campbell's Soup]], [[Discover Card|Discover]], [[Wal-Mart]], [[Nintendo]], [[The University of Texas]], and [[Cisco Systems]].<ref>http://www.peoplepattern.com/</ref>
